MUQuery - MarkUpQuery
An extendable library to allow creating HTML in a context similar to jQuery

Example:
$HTML = new MUQuery();

$page_content .= $HTML->form('/editor/news_edit_update/' . $page . '/')
			->id('ci_admin_edit_form')
			->addClass('simpleForm')
			->attr('style', 'width:600px;')
			->label('submit', ' ')
			->input('submit', 'submit', 'Submit')
			->close()
			->get();